<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.7">
<l>pāmpaṇaimēl pāṟkaṭaluḷ paḷḷi yamarntatuvuṅ</l>
<l>kāmpaṇaitōḷ piṉṉaikkā yēṟuṭaṉēḻ ceṟṟatuvun</l>
<l>tēmpaṇaiya cōlai marāmaramē ḻeytatuvum</l>
<l>pūmpiṇaiya taṇṭuḻāy poṉmuṭiyam pōrēṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He abided on the serpent bed, on the milk ocean bed,</l>
<l>he killed seven bulls together for the sake of Piṉṉai with bamboo-like shoulders,</l>
<l>he shot seven Cadamba trees in the grove with sweet ponds(?),</l>
<l>the battle bull with a gold crown [and] cool Tulsi entwined with flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
